b8a388114443804ec2a1fb104251afa829322b32.name: FlixTrain
b8a388114443804ec2a1fb104251afa829322b32.conditionsSummary: Non-exchangeable. Non-exchangeable. Up to 100% of the ticket price refund in the form of a voucher: issued at 25% of the ticket price for cancellations less than 1 day before departure, 50% between 1 and 6 days, 75% between 7 and 29 days, and 100% for cancellations made 30 days or more in advance. Please visit https://www.flixbus.com/service/change-cancel-a-booking/cancellation-policy. Service fee included in the price and no refundable.
